in</span>、<span class=\"exturl\" data-url=\"aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmlsaWJpbGkuY29tL3ZpZGVvL0JWMVU1NHkxVjdpSi8/c3BtX2lkX2Zyb209Li5zZWFyY2gtY2FyZC5hbGwuY2xpY2smYW1wO3ZkX3NvdXJjZT1hNzk0OWY0OGFkMzA5OGY2YzI2ZjViMGRmZGE4MGIwZA==\">U</span></p>\n<h4 id=\"a-lin\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#a-lin\">#</a> A-Lin</h4>\n<p><span class=\"exturl\" data-url=\"aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmlsaWJpbGkuY29tL3ZpZGVvL0JWMUNCNHkxMTdTay8/c3BtX2lkX2Zyb209Li5zZWFyY2gtY2FyZC5hbGwuY2xpY2smYW1wO3ZkX3NvdXJjZT1hNzk0OWY0OGFkMzA5OGY2YzI2ZjViMGRmZGE4MGIwZA==\">挚友</span>、<span class=\"exturl\" data-url=\"aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmlsaWJpbGkuY29tL3ZpZGVvL0JWMWliNDExMzc2Vi8/c3BtX2lkX2Zyb209Li5zZWFyY2gtY2FyZC5hbGwuY2xpY2smYW1wO3ZkX3NvdXJjZT1hNzk0OWY0OGFkMzA5OGY2YzI2ZjViMGRmZGE4MGIwZA==\">有一种悲伤</span></p>\n<h4 id=\"邓紫棋\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#邓紫棋\">#</a> 邓紫棋</h4>\n<p>每一首都很爱</p>\n<h4 id=\"单依纯\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#单依纯\">#</a> 单依纯</h4>\n<p>All in、爱我的时候、《勇敢额度 album》、好声音 live</p>\n<h4 id=\"beyond\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#beyond\">#</a> beyond</h4>\n<p>灰色轨迹、大地</p>\n<h4 id=\"张信哲\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#张信哲\">#</a> 张信哲</h4>\n<p><span class=\"exturl\" data-url=\"aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmlsaWJpbGkuY29tL3ZpZGVvL0JWMWltNHkxaTdrMT9wPTYmYW1wO3ZkX3NvdXJjZT1hNzk0OWY0OGFkMzA5OGY2YzI2ZjViMGRmZGE4MGIwZA==\">爱就一个字</span>、<span class=\"exturl\" data-url=\"aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmlsaWJpbGkuY29tL3ZpZGVvL0JWMWltNHkxaTdrMT9wPTMzJmFtcDt2ZF9zb3VyY2U9YTc5NDlmNDhhZDMwOThmNmMyNmY1YjBkZmRhODBiMGQ=\">不要对他说</span></p>\n<h4 id=\"太多了基本都是emo歌有空再更樂-哈哈哈哈\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#太多了基本都是emo歌有空再更樂-哈哈哈哈\">#</a> 太多了，基本都是 emo 歌，有空再更，樂、哈哈哈哈</h4>\n<h2 id=\"综艺\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#综艺\">#</a> 综艺</h2>\n<p>天赐的声音、闪光的乐队</p>\n",
